25// Returns properties for the given binary op.
26constexpr Operator::Properties BinopProperties(Operator::Opcode opcode) {
27 DCHECK(JSOperator::IsBinaryWithFeedback(opcode));
28 return opcode == IrOpcode::kJSStrictEqual ? Operator::kPure
29 : Operator::kNoProperties;
30}

32template <class T>
33Address AddressOrNull(OptionalRef<T> ref) {
34 if (!ref.has_value()) return kNullAddress;
35 return ref->object().address();
36}

726// static
727Type JSWasmCallNode::TypeForWasmReturnType(const wasm::ValueType& type) {
728 switch (type.kind()) {
729 case wasm::kI32:
730 return Type::Signed32();
731 case wasm::kI64:
732 return Type::SignedBigInt64();
733 case wasm::kF32:
734 case wasm::kF64:
735 return Type::Number();
736 case wasm::kRef:
737 case wasm::kRefNull:
738 CHECK_EQ(type.heap_type(), wasm::HeapType::kExtern);
739 return Type::Any();
740 default:
741 UNREACHABLE();
742 }
743}
